__*
sysbuild
*.sdf
*.suo
*.sln
*.opensdf
log.txt
extensions
support
build/
build-*/
# Top-level tests dir: track its CMakeLists.txt and the Max test harnesses;
# ignore any scratch/build output. The harnesses live here rather than in
# patchers/ so they are not on Max's package search path and do not ship as if
# they were user-facing modules.
/tests/*
!/tests/CMakeLists.txt
!/tests/patchers/
!/tests/patchers/*
*.o
*.dylib
tmp
.DS_Store
.vs
.claude/

# NOTE: package-info.json is deliberately TRACKED, not ignored. CMake regenerates
# it from package-info.json.in at configure time, but the ReadMe tells users to
# clone straight into Max's Packages folder without building — and without this
# file Max cannot register the package name or the homepatcher, so the Extras
# menu entry never appears. Commit regenerated changes along with any version bump.

# Compiled standalone test executables (keep the .cpp sources)
*_test
test_rpde
*.dSYM/

# Generated test output data
test_output/

# Max/Ableton waveform-analysis sidecar files
*.asd

# Design-system handoff artefacts. The durable reference lives in docs/design/
# (tokens.md is the source of truth for the Paper Lab palette); these are the
# bulky exported bundles and HTML mockups it was derived from.
Strange Pulse Toolkit Design System/
Strange Pulse Toolkit Design System.zip
Strange Pulse Toolkit Redesign.zip
design_handoff_paperlab_ui/

